:param c: java.lang.Class
:return: java.lang.Class<T>
methods.lookupClass:
Finds and caches Class instances based on name. This implementation can handle the strings created by
 Class.getName() and Class.getCanonicalName(), and some mixture of the two. JNI names are not
 supported.

:param name: (java.lang.String) - the name of the class to lookup.
:return: (java.lang.Class<?>) A class instance
